nd you know, and a - a pale blue sailor collar. And one thing I can remember in particular was, I had a pair of black patent shoes on - ankle strap, they had a bit of tin across the toe. I can always remember - isn't it funny, that sticks in my mind. And 
them carrying me - so far, because we had to walk to Lenton. Them carrying me through - Lenton Fields I think it was. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid277430\charrsid12812171 Me }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 
