\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Was anyone paid to help in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No one lived in did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Was the washing done at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes, at home, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did your aunt or uncle do anything in regard to the family's clothes, did they make or mend any clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No, nothing like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Do you know if your own mother did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Well there were none of us able to make anything I don't think. I've missed a lot haven't I, yes. In between. Yes. Well of course
 my mother would mend clothes but she didn't make anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 You were one of the eldest children weren't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 So when you came back home at sixteen there were seven or eight of the others who were younger than you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes. Younger than me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 So you would remember a lot of that sort of period?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 'Cos I went to work as soon as I came home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 What sort of job did you go to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 I went to Boots to start with. Yes. I worked in Parkeson Street. For quite a long time. Then I went
 in to a factory to machining to earn more money. Making blouses and things like that you know. And - well I had several jobs at blouse - making and that sort of thing. Then I went in and worked for a tailor - did some - did the machining in tailoring aft
er I was married.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 When you came back to Beeston, were the clothes in your home mainly new clothes or did the family have secondhand clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Oh they had to have what they could get sort of thing, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 So a lot of the clothes would be secondhand then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Where would they be bought from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Oh that I can't }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid277430\charrsid12812171 tell}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171  you. You see with my mother going out to work into big houses and that sort of thing she often had things given her or bought cheap from - from there you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 And shoes, how did you get on for shoes, do you remember? Did your father help around the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No not much, not very much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Cleaning, cooking, washing up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No, he didn't do anything like that. I don't think men did in those days do you. Not like they do today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Most working men then worked such long hours they didn't have much time did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Well he went all hours I think, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 What about decorating?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4265563\charrsid12812171 No, he didn't - didn't bother, if there's any decorating mother did it.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Or repairs or improvements to the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did he dress or undress or bath you, well you weren't there were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No. I think he helped me mother as much as he could in the house, he was a god father mind you. I remember as
 they didn't do all the world in the house did they.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Can you remember him reading to you or the other children?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Can remember him reading stories to the - other kiddies, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did he tell them stories as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Used to talk to them, was very interesting. And he was very fond of them you know. Very.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did he ever take you out without your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Would he look after you when your mother was out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes, he'd look after the house when mother was out. You see, with me being sixteen I helped to look after them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 What about with your aunt and uncle, were there any basic differences when you lived there, were there any other children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No, I - was the only one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did you have any jobs that you had to carry out a
t home, you wouldn't have in your own home because when you came back from Chatham you went straight to work didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes, but I always helped me mother in the house, what I could.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 So you carried on doing little jobs in the house even after you started work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Oh yes. We all did, we all helped me mother, well the three girls did, always did what we could for her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did you help in the house at Chatham?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes, I had to, I had to a lot. I wasn't - I wasn't very happy there you know. W
asn't quite as nice as it ought to have been. For adoption sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 When you left school in Chatham how old would you be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Well I went to work, when I was fourteen. I must have left then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 What was your first job down there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 In a sweet shop.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Was that the only job you had there?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 
I went - yes, that was the only job I had there. I went another shop belonging the firm like, at Stroud, that's in Chatham, and - then of course I came home after that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 When you came back did your brothers and sisters have normal jobs about the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 
Oh - oh yes, all had to do certain - certain jobs. Either one would wash up and one would dry or - one would make beds or something like that you know. Oh we helped me mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did they continue to do these little tasks about the house even after they left school
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did the older children help the younger with things they found difficult, like dressing, helping the young children to dress and to eat?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Well I can't remember that, you see, I wasn't there was I - were little.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 When you came back were any of your youngest brothers or sisters in that stage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Well I suppose - I don't - I shouldn't - but I suppose really in that light they were all boys you kn
ow. And all the boys - nearly all the boys joined the Boys Brigade when they were very young. And one brother that - who died a few years back, Arthur, he was in the - he went in the brigade when he was eleven or twelve, he went to the first world war wit
h the boys from the brigade, and he was in brigade 'til he died at fifty-five. All those years. He's well known in Beeston for that you know. Everyone called him Officer Johnson sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Were you expected to go to bed at a certain time when you were at school, this would be in Chatham wouldn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Well, was never allowed up late. What you call late.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Who would put you to bed when you lived down there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Can you remember when you first went there if anyone else put you to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Only me auntie that I lived with, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Have you any recollection of about what age you were when you put yourself to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No, no idea, can't remember that far back.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did you share the bedroom with anyone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 You had a bedroom to yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 You had three bedrooms then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 So you'd have one spare bedroom then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Where, in Chatham? Yes, we always had a spare bedroom.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 When you came back here would there be three bedrooms here?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Only three, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 And there'd be quite a lot of you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 
I don't know how the boys used to sleep - I think we had two beds in one - two beds in each room like and - of course I was at home quite a while when - me other sisters was born if you understand me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 What room did you bath in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 We had to bath in front of the fire. No bath then you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 This was in Chatham and in Beeston?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 How often did you have a bath in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Once a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Was it customary to have clean clothes on }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4265563\charrsid12812171 bath night}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Oh yes. We was always kept clean, always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 These }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4265563\charrsid12812171 sorts}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171  of customs were the same at your auntie's house and at home were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes, oh yes. Yes, regular.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 I think we'd better keep to the Chatham part, where did the family have their meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 
Well, at home - I used to - me uncle used to have his dinners always - at the dock - yard, 'cos I used to take them. And - I had mine before I went. Then went straight to school. Teatime of course we always had tea together. Just the three of us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 In the living room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Were there any occasions when there would be eating taking place in any other room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Special occasions? Where did your auntie cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 What sort of cooking equipment was it?
