Well she had a fireplace. Fireplace and oven in the back kitchen, in the third - in the kitchen. There'd be kitchen, living room and a front room as }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4265563\charrsid12812171 they'd}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171  call it then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did she have a range or gas stove?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No, a range. Fire.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 When was breakfast eaten?
