\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Oh yes. Yes. I wasn't kept - down like that.
