Well I don't know what to say about that, me auntie used to grumble at me, but me mother never did. So I don't think I could have been so bad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did you get your ideas about behaviour more from your aunt than your uncle and more from your mother than your father?
