Well - me aunt was very strict with me but - me mother, I think I got it better from me mother, she was more gentle about things. If you didn't do anything right she'd tell you you hadn't done it right you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 If you had a birthday was it a different day to any other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid277430\charrsid12812171 With}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 
 me aunt she used to let me have one or two for tea. But not a party, I didn't never - never knew what a party was. And of course when I came home me mother wasn't well enough off to have a party for any of us.
