n used to go up the cherry tree and snatch the cherries off and throw 'em into your - lap. Little things like that I can remember, stand out. You take the pinafore }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid277430\charrsid12812171 off}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
