\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 What did you think about that, did you ever think about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Oh - yes,
 I did, I used to feel very sorry about it and - well we used to help me mother as much as we possible could, but - with having a lot of children my mother was very poor. Very, you know what I mean, and she'd go out washing, cleaning or - ironing at home 
for anybody - or nursing or anything - to make ends meet. To pay her way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 What difference did it make to the family when your father was ill or out of work?
