 yes, we were all pals together sort of thing and - helped - helped each other, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 How often was your father out of work, can you remember?
