Eriksson\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171  - switchboards used to go to the racing tracks you see, they fitted them up there, so he was foreman on that, on them. And the
n the - the racing association bought him over - from }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14222938\charrsid12812171 Eriksson\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 
