 And it was very nice, there was only about eight or nine of us in it you see. And it was very nice, I liked that very much. Mind you I didn't start off in that, I started off as an ordinary examiner on the bench with the reminder, but I got picked for a 
little special job and it - from one little job I got to another sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did you s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14222938\charrsid12812171 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 rve an apprenticeship?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Or training period for any of your jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No. Nothing. I must have been clever. Well, I mean, I can - adapt myself to life.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did you belong to any trade union?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did you feel that employers and workers had the same interests or different interests?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No I don't think so, I got on ever so well with - everybody at work, specially Everlastic. Very we
ll, that was the manageress as came yesterday, and I've been left eleven years. She does - she comes every now and again you see, surprises me. But - and I - and there's quite a few of the - the girls still come that I worked with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did you ever feel that there was a division of interest amongst the workers themselves
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 In what way? I don't know what you mean really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Some workers would operate a different way of working, a sort of a select group, you know what I mean, and they would feel their 
interests were different to another group of workers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 
Well of course there would be in groups in a factory like that, all doing different jobs. I don't think one thought they was any different to another really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 In the old days going back to the
 pre first world war time in those days, were you ever aware of a great division between trained craftsmen and other types of workers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No, I never used to feel like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 You weren't aware that anybody else did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Would you say that full time work changed your attitude to life in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 
No, because I've always been very fond of going to work. And if I was able now I'd go. I like company you see. And I - I love going to work, I - I've always liked every job I've got - had, I'v
e always liked it. Perhaps some better than others. But I've always got on all right, got on well with everybody, and I've always liked going. When I left - this one I - I nearly broke me heart. When I left Everlastic. They bought me a gold watch when I l
eft.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 After you left school you continued to live at home didn't you, you lived with your aunt?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Then you came back to Beeston?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 And you lived at home while you were at work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did doing full time work change your relationship with your parents at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Or your brothers and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did you spend your Sunday any differently as a worker than as a schoolchild, did you do anything different on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 I - I joined the - t
he parish church and was confirmed at the parish church and I used to go to church and perhaps a Sunday school as well now and again like but - not made a regular habit of - going.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 But you maintained your interest in it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Even though you'd left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did you ever take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No. Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 
You were married before 1918 weren't you? You were telling me a earlier something of how you spent your spare time, did you continue to spend your spa
re time in the same way or did you do things differently now, did you spend your spare time in a different way now you'd left school and started work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No, I don't think so, used to go dancing a bit or - anything like that. In the evening you know. Perhaps about once a week, that's all.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Who with?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Me sisters and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did you make any new friends, boys or girls at this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No, I - the man I married, I went with him when I was about - seventeen I think. And I was married when I was t
wenty-two. And he was the only one I had sort of thing. I used to have plenty of boys you know, you do don't you. Boys and girls, but I only had him really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did you ever bring friends home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Do you mean at me mother's home? Not very often because there was such a crowd of us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 What about in }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14222938\charrsid12812171 Chatham}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 We used to have one or two friends in but - they didn't allow me to have much - any parties or anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did you have any special friends at this time, immediately after leaving school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Boy or girl?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No, nobody special.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did your parents meet your friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Meet them? Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did your aunt and uncle meet your friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No, they wasn't very interested.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did they expect to know where you were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Oh yes. Yes. Mind they were pretty strict on me sort of -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 You would have to be home by a special time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 By a certain time and all that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 You were twenty-two when you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 You'd known your husband then for five years?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14222938\charrsid12812171 Known him a long, long time.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 How did you meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Well it's very funny, just walking along the High Road. Yes. Just walked along, you know, how you stand and talk and that sort of thing.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Where did he come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Beeston.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did you have save up money before you got married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Save up? I couldn't 'cos I didn't earn enough to save mine but he did, he was - we started with a nice little home all paid for.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did your parents help you in setting up the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No, not to buy - well, yes, they did in a way. But - not expensive things. Mother helped me with - linen and stuff like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Out of that five years how long were you engaged?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 To be very candid I never had an engagement ring. See thi
s ring I've got on now? I had that bought - he bought me that when I'd been married quite a few years, 'cos I didn't have one. And I've had it ever since. And I've worn it ever since you see. Yes. Well we were going to engage - I were going to have an eng
agement and this is how it happened. And - went down Nottingham to buy it, and we saw some furniture in a window. And we thought it were best spent on that. That was what we did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Could you describe the wedding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes I can do. It was Christmas Day.
 Yes. Christmas Day, and it was a beautiful day, the sun shone and I know I was in white of course with all }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14222938\charrsid12812171 paraphernalia}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 
, you know, and - only thinking about it, I wasn't a bit cold, so it couldn't have been a very cold day and my mother was ill at the ti
me so we had to - keep the wedding up at my husband's mother's and that was just - that was in Beeston, and we had quite a nice time, but I didn't have a honeymoon. No. We spent the money in the house instead you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Was it a church wedding?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Y
es. No - story. It wasn't, it should have been but they wouldn't marry me on Christmas Day. And the uncle that brought me up, I told you that he - I - brought up by an uncle, he said he was coming to give me away you see, instead of me father. And he came
 up from Chatham to give me away, that day, and the church would not marry on Christmas Day. So I was married at the church on Tuwell Road. The Wesleyan church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 You had guests to the wedding did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes, friends you know and our own family and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 And presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes, I had quite a lot of bits bought me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 But you didn't go away for a honeymoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Where did you live after you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Derby Street. In Beeston.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 How many years did you live in that house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 
I lived in there 'til - I knew that I was going to have a baby. And - why I left it I don't know but I went back to it eventually, and I went into a little bit bigger house in Willerby Street, Beeston. And - then my eldest boy - the baby was poorly an
d the doctor said, you've left - you've left the most healthiest street in Beeston when you left Derby Street. And there was a house to let on the opposite }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14222938\charrsid12812171 side}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171  and I got it back again. So I went back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 You say you were in that house until you were expecting your first child, that was for about two years was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Then you went to somewhere else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Willerby Street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 And then you came back to Derby Street?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Back again to Derby Street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 How long did you live in Derby Street then?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 
I - the war broke - the second war. No, no. The first war my husband went to the war. That was in Derby Street. And I had to go to work to help to keep going, and my mother had the children so I gave the house up. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 You gave the house up during the war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Where did you live then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Lived with my mother. Yes. And then - after the war - I went - I got a house up }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14222938\charrsid12812171 Grove}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171  Avenue, Chilwell. Do you know it all? Opposite Bartons, opposite }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14222938\charrsid12812171 Barton\rquote s}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 So that took you up to the end of the war anyway, back with your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 How old was your husband when you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 He's a year older than me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 And you were twenty-two?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 So he'd be twenty-three wouldn't he.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 What was your husband's job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 He was a lace draughtsman. Designer draughtsman.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 When you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did he have other jobs before that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No, he went to that - I think he was at school }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14222938\charrsid12812171 till}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171  he were about sixteen and then he went into - as an apprentice you see for this, in Beeston, served his apprenticeship. And eventually he got to be - a manager of so many lace machines at Stapleford for }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14222938\charrsid12812171 Widowson's}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171  of Beeston that used to be. Well when they came back from the war - the - the old gentleman he wor
ked for - old Mr Widowson, wouldn't carry on - couldn't carry on and the lads wouldn't take to it, you see, so that was given up. So then he was out of work. And he went into the Income Tax offices for a time. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 This was about 1920 time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Afte
r the war. And - he went in the Income Tax offices for a time and - and eventually one way or another, he did a bit of lace work, lace - you know, designing and draughting for different places, and then he eventually landed up where I'd been traveling for
 you see. Yes. Well the lace trade had gone you see.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 So he worked for Inland Revenue for a bit, then he did a bit of .....?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Managing, furniture manager.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Furniture manager?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 You said he did a bit of lace designing again, would that be on a casual basis?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 
To be very candid he - he - did some for Germany. He'd have sent it by post I suppose, rolled it up in a - sent it by post and that used to help through, 'cos he was out of work some time. And he did a bit, and I don't thi
nk he was supposed to have done it you see those days. But he did it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 This would be in the '20's?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 So this sort of supplemented his income?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 It helped us, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 How did your husband feel about - you were working at the same time weren't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes. Round about that time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 How did your husband feel about you working, did he have any feelings about you going out at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No, he didn't used to bother - he used to know that I liked it and I was quite happy and he didn't bother then. 'Cos he'd be home all day.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 How do you think your husband felt about his work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 He liked his own trade. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Do you think he felt a bit resentful about having to give it up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Well he - he was really because he'd - served hi
s time at it and one thing and another and - it was a bit hard, but still it couldn't be helped, everybody was the same - in the lace trade weren't they. But he was pretty well educated that he could almost take - anything. Yes. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 You had children didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Two boys.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 One was born 1910?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 
One born in 1908 - would have been born 1910 wouldn't he. Then the other one was born thirteen months after that. So I had two close together you see. One's fifty-nine and one's sixty. One at fifty-nine was here last night. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Were they born at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did you know what to expect in childbirth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Oh me mother used to talk to me 'cos she was so used to - the job you see, and also she looked after me at the time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 How did you get on in the actual birth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Oh all right, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 So your mother was the main help to you was she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did you have any outside medical help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Doctors of course, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did your husband help at all at the births?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 How soon were you out of bed after giving birth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Fortnight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did you get up for the whole day then or gradually?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Well I think I got up you see, they used to have to stay in bed so long didn't they those days and - it was ten day
s supposed to be, but I was in bed a fortnight, me mother was looking after me. So that when I did get up I was up sort of thing.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 So your mother was running the show while you were actually in bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did anyone else apart from your mother help you at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 
Well over Eric, the first one, I had a - a person in to keep the house - keep house and - and look after me - in between me mother coming up and down sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did you have a nurse?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes, I had a nurse over the - second one, my husband was out of work when he was born, and - had a district nurse come in and me mother.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 The district nurse just used to pop in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 For how long?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Once a day you see. Just for }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid277430\charrsid12812171 \endash }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid277430\charrsid12812171 well,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171  to attend to me, that was all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 For how long did she come?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Oh - oh I see what you mean. Oh only until I got up, then she - never - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 What did the nurse do for the baby then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 She used to wash him, dress him, sort of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Can you tell me how you fed your first baby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Well I breast fed the first one. But not for very long. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14222938\charrsid12812171 
And I started to feed the next one but I was always very, very - thin sort of thing, there was nothing about me much, and the doctor took me off it - took him off it and put him on to tinned food you see.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did you enjoy feeding the baby yourself or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Well I did, it was less trouble than anything else wasn't it really. But - it's not quite so convenient I don't think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 So the doctor took you off and you went onto .....?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Why
 - those days it was - it - the last one was - is very rosy faced now, rosy bonny lad - bonny baby and - when the doctor came he asked me, he said is it - how did I feed him, and I told him and he said - twelve o'clock at night and I said, oh he's just dr
o
pped to sleep. He said, well wake him up, I'm not coming out at this time of night to know, you know. So of course I did and he said, will it be his feeding time? I said, yes, it will. And I went to feed him and all he said was, put it away, put it away. 
See? And I said, well - what am I to do? He says, get some }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14222938\charrsid12812171 Witchell's}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 
 food. It's sixpence a packet. And it was. Sixpence a packet those days. This food it was - ordinary packet like that. He said, it's cheap, it's the cheapest there is, but it's plenty good enough for him. He meant he was strong you see. }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14222938\charrsid12812171 And I fed him on that, then he finished him off with - he came one day again, he weren't very well I suppose, and I said he was on Witchell's food still. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 He said, well no, take him off that and put him onto - Scotch oatmeal. And he was finished off on scotch oatmeal. With the bottle but - he's never - he's never }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14222938\charrsid12812171 ailed}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171  anything, only just cold or anything.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 You didn't really have any difficulties with feeding did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Oh no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 If you wanted advice during that early time of motherhood who did you ask for advice?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Mother I suppose.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 If the baby was asleep would you wake him for a feed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 What about if he cried before the normal feeding time, would you feed him then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Well I - I used to do a bit I think because I hadn't got ever such a lot you see so - have to sort of do best I could.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 What did you do if he was crying but didn't seem hungry?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Don't know, used to nurse him. I never let them cry much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 When did he first have solid food?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Oh I can't remember. Didn't used to give babies solid - solid food those days you know. Not 'til they were getting on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 You weaned them at what sort of age, can you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No, I can't remember.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Was it gradual weaning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes, oh yes, gradually.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did the baby seem to mind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No. Oh I used to feed him on rusks I can remember that. Rusks with a spoon you know and milk and - a bottle in between sort of thing.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did you think at that time that it did the baby any harm to let him cry or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Well I didn't used to let him cry to be very candid. Not much, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did you ever punish him if he was naughty?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Not when he was tiny, no. They've never had many good hidings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did your husband ever have anything to do with the babies when they were very small, under one year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 
Well - now it wasn't much in his line to be very candid, he was brought up by a grandma and an only one there you see, so he wasn't much used to babies. But as they toddled about and he was very interested then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did he ever bath them or change their nappies when they were little?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No, oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 But he would play with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Play with them. And - the - the young - the eldest one, he was only a little 
toddler just toddling about and - a man came to the door once and said to him - to my husband, is your son in? So of course he - he }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14222938\charrsid12812171 laughed}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171  you see, and he said, well I've got two, which is the one you want? Well one was the baby and - Eric was just toddle
r, only a year older. And he says, yes, had said, I have two sons, which did you want? He said, I think they call him Eric. He said, yes. Eric. Oh, he said, what did you want him for? So he says, he's been and broken three panes of glass in my - cold fram
e
. So he said, has he really? Oh dear. So of course my husband thought it were a feat - you see. And he says, Eric, come here, I want you. Eric come toddling out the front you know and he says, this is my son, he says, that isn't the one as broke the frame
s
. He said, well this is the only one I've got. So he said to him, have you - smashed this gentleman's glass with a stick? He says, mm, big stick. And he had done. Yes, he'd smashed them you see with a stick. And I can remember it cost my husband three shi
llings. He said it were best three bob he ever spent, thought it were wonderful.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did he ever put them to bed when they were very small?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Oh yes, he'd help to put them to bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Would he attend to them in the night if they woke up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes, he would do, he'd help me with them like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did he ever take them out without you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes. Very often - Sunday mornings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did you know what your husband earned?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 How much would he give you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 When I first got married I had twenty-four shillings a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did you discuss with your husband how it should be spent?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 
But I can't - yes, oh yes, we'd talk it over and how we'd spend it and all that sort of thing. And if he'd got any money he'd always help me out or - anything like that you know, but - I never got into }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid277430\charrsid12812171 debt}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171  or anything. 'Course you couldn't get into debt those days, you couldn't afford to. But - he was a good husband, it's no good saying he wasn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 How many rooms were in the house you had in Derby Street?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Six. Two bedrooms, attic, back kitchen, living room and front room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Were there any relatives or lodgers living with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Was there any paid help in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Was the washing done at home or was it sent out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No, do it at home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did you make or mend clothes?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Well I used to make all the babies - all the kiddies clothes always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Were the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14222938\charrsid12812171 children\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171  clothes new or secondhand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Oh new. I used to - buy a bit of stuff and - being used to being a machinist I could soon - make them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 If they had bought clothes where would they be bought from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Well I don't know, anywhere where - you saw anything. According like -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 You didn't have one special place?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Were they bought when they were needed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did your husband make any shoes or repair them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No. No. We bought shoes. No, we used to have - Startrite shoes you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did your husband help with jobs in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No, that wasn't much in his line that wasn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Cleaning or cooking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Washing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 He - he'd help me wash the pots but - he wasn't any good at anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Not decorating?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No. Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Or improvements to the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 I don't think he could use a - hammer and nail or anything like that you know, my meaning. He could use a pen but that were about it.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did he help with dressing or undressing the children?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes, he'd help that way, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Reading to them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes. And play with them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did he ever bath them at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No. I don't remember him doing that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Tell them stories?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes, if ever - when it was their birthdays we had little parties and he'd always - amuse the children while they were there you know.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 You said he did take them out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Would he look after them if you had to go out somewhere?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 As your children grew up did they have any little jobs that you expected them to do around the house regular jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No I don't think so, unless it was an errand to run or anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 What time did the children go to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 About eight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did they go by themselves or did one of you put them to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Oh no, we always took them to bed, they - saw they was -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Who would take them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 I either would or Billie would, either of us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did the boys share a bed or bedroom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Shared a bed. -A double bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 You'd got three bedrooms there hadn't you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 So there'd be one spare wouldn't there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Well it was an attic you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 You and your husband had the other room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 We had the other double bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 What room was used for having a bath?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Hadn't got a bathroom you know. Kitchen, back kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 When would they be bathed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Well I used to bath the babies - as kiddies - most days. But we would have one - Sunday afternoon or Sunday evening.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 When did the children have clean clothes then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Oh dear, about every day I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Where were meals eaten?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 In the living room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Any occasions when you had meals in another room in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Where did you cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 What on, a range?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No. Stove - gas stove.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 When was breakfast eaten?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 When we'd got time to eat it you mean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Was it a rush in the morning then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 
Oh yes, it'd be early, because the kiddies would have to go to school and I was going to work and - and he was, so we should all be - dashing about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did you have breakfast all together then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No, we didn't, we had to have it in bits.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 So your husband would be out first?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 He'd be out first. Then the children. Then I went last.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Who used to get the meal ready?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Oh I had to do that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 What did you usually have for breakfast on an ordinary weekday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Why toast or an egg or - bit of bacon or - all depends how the money went I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 What sort of drink would you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Tea, cocoa the kiddies used to have.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Was Sunday any different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 What about the midday meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 
Well the kiddies used to go to me mother's. For their midday meal. And he was out at work and I was, so we used to - take sandwiches or something like - and have something when we got home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 What about Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Oh we always had meals together on Sunday, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Would that be a different sort of meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Well I suppose it would be a little bit - you'd have a joint wouldn't you those days
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Was the breakfast different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No, not a deal.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 What about evening meals then, did you all sit down together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 For tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 What you usually have to eat and drink for tea then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 
Well I don't - I can't - cakes or - something the kids fancied really you know. Or me husband used to be very fond of - an herring or something like that you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Was Sunday tea any different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Oh we might have a tin of something for Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did you go in for making bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Jam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Pickles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No. I've never liked cooking much. I cook ordinary food but I mean I've never been one to - do anything special.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did your husband do anything like making wine?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Or beer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Medicines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Bottling fruit or vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did you grow any vegetables or fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Well we might grow just potatoes or something like that, greens, that was all.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 You bought the rest did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did you buy tinned or dried vegetables or fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No. Fresh vegetables.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 You can't remember tinned or dried stuff?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did you keep any pigs or hens or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Can you remember how many times a week you would eat meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Well I don't know I'm sure how - how many times the kiddies would have it when they was with me mother, but I s
hould have - we should have meat when they were at home every day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 What about tinned meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Was there ever any extra obtained from poaching?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Poach. No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did you ever have to go short so that your husband and children could have more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No - I might if there was anything nice and - they wanted it sort of thing, I'd go without then but - not in the general way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did your husband need to have larger helpings of food than anybody else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No. Had less than me. He 
didn't eat much. He didn't eat big meals, I mean? I don't mean to say he didn't eat much, but if you put too much on his plate he used to say, oh don't give me a lot. You see. And only wanted - small amounts to eat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Were your children allowed to talk during meals or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Well they were stopped if they did begin to talk.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Were they allowed to choose what they wanted to eat from what was cooked or did they have to eat some of everything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Well - I don't think they used to be bothered, I used to give them a - give them a meal you know and - that was that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 What was your attitude if some food was left uneaten on the plate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Well I didn't used to bother, if they didn't want it they didn't eat it. If they'd had enough.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did they wait for things on the table to be passed to them or would they ask for something if they wanted it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 They'd ask for it, could they have it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did they ask for second helpings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Oh if they wanted it they'd ask for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Were they taught to hold their knife and - fork in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Oh yes, proper mannered.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Were they permitted to bring toys or a book to the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Not at mealtimes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 When did members of the family leave the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 When - they'd ask if they could leave the table when they'd finished their meal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 When you were all there did you all sit together at the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Did you have regular places at the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Yes, all had our own seats, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Who would serve the meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 Was there any special order in which you served it?
