\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11943414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 When the children were very young and couldn't sit on their own at the table, would they sit at the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1466171 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5993906\charrsid12812171 In a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14222938\charrsid12812171 highchair}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
